scene_description_enriched: The scene depicts an angel with feathered wings, holding a bow and arrow, reaching towards a seated figure. The seated figure, possibly a woman, is wearing a halo and appears to be holding something in their hands. Behind the seated figure is a tree with leaves. The background is filled with small dots, suggesting a starry or celestial setting. The overall composition is framed by decorative elements, possibly part of a larger manuscript illumination.
